de.tub.similarity
Class Sequence<E>

java.lang.Object
  de.tub.similarity.Sequence<E>

public class Sequence<E>
extends Object

The Sequence class is backed by a LinkedList and can be used in connection with the SequenceCluster to map a sequence of clusters visited by a user.

Author:
Sebastian Oelke
See Also:
SequenceCluster, LinkedList
